title: Large 1bed plus office room. In-Unit laundry in North Square North End
posting_body: ['Available September 1st', 'Address: 14 North Square Boston, MA 02113.', 'Open concept kitchen-living room, Extra high ceiling, Two large windows facing on Freedom Trail at historic North Square in North End.', 'You can see Paul Revere House, pebble stones from windows.', 'Living room/kitchen:', 'Restored original hardwood floors and oak paneling walls, built-in antique glass hutch and wall mounted china cabinet.', 'New cherry wood cabinet with extra deep sink, garbage disposal, modern faucet, vanilla creme quartz counters, brand new high quality stainless steel appliances: full size gas range/oven, dishwasher, extra large over the range microwave with built-in fan, and refrigerator.', 'Bathroom: Renovated bathroom with an antique cabinet that has a lot of linen closet space, new beige granite counter and modern sink and faucet, toilet with white marble mosaic floors.', 'All new modern stand shower room with grey porcelain wall and floor with modern fixture in separate room.', "Bedroom: Large bedroom that's spacious enough to put a king size bed, new spacious closet, ceiling fan/light with wall mount control.", 'Bonus room/office:', "There's separate bonus room that can be use as a home office.", "There's also in-unit washer and dryer.", 'Nearby Public Transportation', 'Blue', '0.29 mi at Aquarium Station (183 State Street, Boston)', 'Green', 'Orange', '0.30 mi at Haymarket Station (Congress Street at New Sudbury Street, Boston)', 'Blue', 'Orange', '0.40 mi at State Station (200 Washington Street and 1 State Street, Boston)', 'Green', 'Blue', '0.45 mi at Government Center Station (Tremont Street at Court Street at Cambridge Street, Boston)', 'Red', 'Green', '0.69 mi at Park Street Station (Tremont Street at Park Street at Winter Street, Boston)', 'Call Daniel 617-899-8529']
